{"tid":672562,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：九龍城 chicken n egg","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T07:12:18.000Z","uid":181719,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2627e070541193b810fc384ba9478d2942092f05","tid":672562,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"最近又一次去九龍城諗住食泰菜，結果又失敗咗，因為經過呢間野，見佢個原味雞同醬烤骨拼盤好似幾吸引，結果泰國菜又要等下次喇。<br />\n<br />\n上菜之後係有啲失望嘅，因為半隻雞，本來諗住好豐富，點知成隻乳鴿咁細，食落口感亦唔特別香口，最多話佢好住家風味咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/140820_a554a21c55162c3f74aee7d8157ec32c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F140820_a554a21c55162c3f74aee7d8157ec32c.jpeg&h=ccd752aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放枝叉喺隔離睇吓有幾細隻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/140841_61abaaa12a1fca6f9318df40209f5e26.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F140841_61abaaa12a1fca6f9318df40209f5e26.jpeg&h=948fd4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醬烤骨份量比烤雞多啲，但想像中用醬醃過去烤嘅效果，現實係烤完之後查醬上面啫...可能有啲人中意呢種食法，但我就覺得比較求其啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/140959_e9a8edb9c94f64ccd297fde0414211b5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F140959_e9a8edb9c94f64ccd297fde0414211b5.jpeg&h=b1bf245b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇醬果邊就唔夠味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141023_e7ec946d3f63a89369ca4e8be2b36baf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141023_e7ec946d3f63a89369ca4e8be2b36baf.jpeg&h=70873950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡邦尼意粉就中規中矩，亦都唔覺特別好食。最後兩個人唔夠飽，嗌多個朱古力批食吓，反而有驚喜喎。呢啲朱古力蛋糕 / mousse 類嘅野，通常都係濃味得黎好膩，或者清淡得滯兩條出路嘅，而呢度嘅朱古力夠濃味得黎，密度唔會太高 / 太膠固，所以好食得黎又唔膩喎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141122_9db7593bb47910a192d31789af9f4abd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141122_9db7593bb47910a192d31789af9f4abd.jpeg&h=05d3cde3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141128_9f4c8534c623503e135c6157b6e6d3bd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141128_9f4c8534c623503e135c6157b6e6d3bd.jpeg&h=3c3ea363&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141134_94cdc88a9d8903bb6bfc9a19cc19c78d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141134_94cdc88a9d8903bb6bfc9a19cc19c78d.jpeg&h=83cc0708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括而言，佢招牌菜唔太出色，似乎亦唔多客，轉做甜品可能仲好啲......<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141251_3b379d7a8d8ba76d163de6ee83b60267.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141251_3b379d7a8d8ba76d163de6ee83b60267.jpeg&h=47aeb128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/141258_18d9017167d79a2d93ef7f03c1e4df68.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F141258_18d9017167d79a2d93ef7f03c1e4df68.jpeg&h=39a9f7ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a5d293a5d7b8e3941c86ed46aa3b52487012046","tid":672562,"uid":20784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2627e070541193b810fc384ba9478d2942092f05","tid":672562,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"